---
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
import Divider from "../components/Divider.astro";
import Title from "../components/Title.astro";
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout>
  <section class="py-[1.5em]">
    <p>Hola, Hello, こんにちは, Salut, Hallo, 안녕하세요.</p>
    <p class="mt-4">
      My full name is Nauzet Aduen Hernández Hernández, I'm a Software Engineer
      based in Gran Canaria, Spain.
    </p>
  </section>
  <Divider />
  <section class="py-[1.5em]">
    <Title text="Work" />
    <p>
      In 2022, worked at <a class="underline" href="https://www.barkibu.com"
        >Barkibu</a
      >
       helping develop the mobile app in Flutter. Worked in every area, from
      backend, in Ruby on Rails, to devops, with Bitrise, Heroku, etc.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4">
      In 2021, worked at <a class="underline" href="https://adedelivered.com"
        >ADE</a
      > where I helped develop a webapp in React aimed at helping companies in
      the mobility sector adapt to the new e-mobility landscape.
    </p>
  </section>

  <Divider />

  <section class="py-[1.5em]">
    <Title text="Tech" />
    <p>
      Have a Degree in Computer Engineering with an intesification in Software
      Engineering by the <a
        class="underline"
        href="https://www.ulpgc.es"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank">ULPGC</a
      >.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4">
      Focused in mobile development, specifically in Flutter, with around 3
      years of experience.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4">
      Love to learn new tech and be the first adapter and then forget about it.
    </p>
    <Button
      href="https://www.github.com/NauzetAduen"
      text="Visit my github"
      external="true"
    />
  </section>
  <Divider />
  <section class="py-[1.5em]">
    <Title text="Personal" />
    <p>
      Some of my hobbies are learning the guitar and the bass, <a
        href="https://www.chess.com/member/nowset"
        class="underline">playing chess</a
      > and working out.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-4">
      Far into the past, played football, basketball and videogames for years.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4">Diabetic type I, broken too many bones, sleeps poorly.</p>
  </section>
  <Divider />
</MainLayout>
